snippet.title: Roselia - "BLACK SHOUT" (Difficulty: Hard 7.0) Gameplay
snippet.description:
With its energetic and strong melody, Roselia's "BLACK SHOUT" is definitely a song you do not want to miss when playing BanG Dream! Girls Band Party!
